div.div: /fabricator/add_job : POST (Add a new job to a fabricator queue)
/fabricator/remove_job?job_id=id&fabricator_id=id : DELETE (Delete a job from a fabricator queue)
/fabricator/register : POST (Attempt to register a new fabricator into the db)
/fabricator/edit_job_status : PATCH (Edit status of the current job)
/fabricator/prioritize_job: PATCH (Move a job to the front of the queue)
/fabricator/edit_name : PATCH (Edit the name of a fabricator)
/fabricator/rerun_job : POST (Rerun the previous job in the queue)
/fabricator/release_job : POST (Tells the fabricator to run the current job on the queue)
/fabricator/get_registered : GET (Returns all of the fabricators that are currently registered)
/fabricator/get_all : GET (Returns all of the fabricators that the backend recognizes)
